msgstr "Oto efekt końcowy:"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/vector_classification/label_tool.rst:264
msgid ""
"As you can see, this hides some labels that were previously visible, because"
" of the difficulty of making some of them follow twisting street lines while"
" still being legible. It makes other labels much more useful since they "
"track the roads rather than float in space between them. You can decide "
"which of these options to use, depending on what you think seems more useful"
" or what looks better."
msgstr ""
"Opcja ta powoduje ukrycie niektórych widocznych wcześniej etykiet, ponieważ "
